<p begin="00:00:06.974" end="00:00:09.343" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Stephen: WELCOME BACK, </span><span style="block">EVERYBODY.</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:09.343" end="00:00:11.812" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MY GUEST TONIGHT IS A </span><span style="block">THEORETICAL PHYSICIST WHO'S </span><span style="block">WRITTEN A NEWSWEEK </span><span style="block">ARTICLE ENTITLED "ASTEROID</span></p>



