<p begin="00:03:38.919" end="00:03:41.755" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; THE RUSSIANS HAVE TAKEN THIS </span><span style="block">SERIOUSLY.</span></p>

<p begin="00:03:41.755" end="00:03:44.358" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Stephen: OF COURSE, THEY </span><span style="block">WOULD.</span></p>

<p begin="00:03:44.358" end="00:03:45.659" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THEY ALMOST GOT TAGGED.</span></p>
<p begin="00:03:45.659" end="00:03:51.365" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; THEY SAID WE HAVE TO MAINTAIN </span><span style="block">SERIOUS PROPALS.</span></p>

<p begin="00:03:51.365" end="00:03:57.137" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MAYBE IN 2029 --</span></p>
