<p begin="00:04:01.275" end="00:04:06.947" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; FIRST YOU HAVE TO LAND ON IT, </span><span style="block">PUT A ROCKET ON IT AND THE </span><span style="block">ROCKET WILL PUSH IT SLIGHTLY OUT</span></p>


