<p begin="00:04:49.156" end="00:04:54.094" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; YES, UP WANT TO KEEP IT IN </span><span style="block">TAFNLGT WE'RE GOING TO BE </span><span style="block">LOOKING AT IT VERY CAREFULLY TO</span></p>


